The Service Provider agrees to perform the following services (the "Services") for the Client:

{{service_description}}

The Service Provider shall perform the Services in a professional and competent manner, consistent with generally accepted industry standards and practices.

The Client shall:

(a) Provide the Service Provider with timely access to all information, materials, and resources reasonably necessary for the performance of the Services;
(b) Designate a representative to serve as the primary point of contact;
(c) Review and provide feedback on deliverables within a reasonable timeframe;
(d) Make payments in accordance with the terms of this Agreement.
